---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Vaelinya and Merrin W. Dream.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About Vaelinya</h1>
    <p class="lede">Vaelinya is a colourful, illustrated, learnable story world created by Merrin W. Dream.</p>
    <p>It is built as a public adventure doorway: stories first, then world, language, and artefacts that deepen understanding without forcing readers to study before they begin.</p>
    <p>The full working canon remains private in MainVault. This site holds the public-facing world.</p>
    <div class="link-list">
      <a href="/read/">Begin with stories</a>
      <a href="/world/">Explore the world</a>
      <a href="/language/">Learn the language</a>
      <a href="/artefacts/">See artefacts</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
